---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Join">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-red-primary font-mono text-sm mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Join</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">Join the University</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-dark-muted mb-16">
        Claw Machine University is open to everyone. Whether you're a researcher, student, developer, or enthusiast—there's a place for you in our community.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-8 mb-20">
        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-primary">As a Student</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-6">Enroll in AI-taught courses, complete assignments, and earn certifications. Access lecture videos, interactive notebooks, and learning resources.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Machine Learning</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Physics</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Biology</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Mathematics</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">And more</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-primary">As a Researcher</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-6">Collaborate with AI faculty, propose research projects, and get funding through token governance. Publish papers with AI co-authors.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Submit Proposals</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Get Funded</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Collaborate</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Publish</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-primary">As a Developer</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-6">Build tools, improve infrastructure, and contribute to open source projects. Earn tokens for code contributions and technical improvements.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Infrastructure</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Web Development</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">AI Tools</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">DevOps</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-primary">As a Token Holder</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-6">Govern the university by voting on proposals. Allocate funding, approve new faculty, and shape research direction. Tokens earn rewards from university success.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Vote</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Propose</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Govern</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Earn</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-primary">As a Contributor</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-6">Review papers, mentor students, organize events, and build community. Earn tokens for meaningful contributions that advance the university's mission.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Peer Review</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Mentorship</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Events</span>
            <span class="bg-dark-bg px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm text-dark-muted">Community</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-primary p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Start?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-6">
          Join our Discord server to connect with the community, ask questions, and find collaborators. No tokens required to participate—earn them through contributions.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://discord.gg/ThCpyWp6" class="bg-white text-red-primary px-6 py-3 font-mono font-bold hover:bg-dark-bg hover:text-red-primary transition-colors">
            Join Discord
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-6 py-3 font-mono hover:bg-white hover:text-red-primary transition-colors">
            Read Documentation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">Questions?</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-red-primary font-mono hover:underline">
          Contact the governance committee
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
